          <p>RemoveTrailingWhitespaceCheck: { }</p>
          <p>RemoveUnusedMethodsInControllersCheck: { except_methods: [] }</p>
          <p>RemoveUnusedMethodsInHelpersCheck: { except_methods: [] }</p>
