          <p>SimplifyRenderInControllersCheck: { }</p>
          <p>SimplifyRenderInViewsCheck: { }</p>
          <p>#UseBeforeFilterCheck: { customize_count: 2 }</p>
          <p>UseModelAssociationCheck: { }</p>
          <p>UseMultipartAlternativeAsContentTypeOfEmailCheck: { }</p>
